HEAT 1/2 tsp. of the oil in large nonstick skillet on medium heat. Add peppers, onions and chili powder; cook and stir 5 minutes or until tender-crisp. Remove from pan. ADD remaining 1/2 tsp. oil to skillet. Add cheeseburgers; cook 4 minutes. Turn burgers; top with vegetables. Cook an additional 4 minutes; cut in half. PLACE 2 burger halves on each tortilla; top with vegetables.